{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_bdrk_016WeL5FuhndScHFuSyyFHrX","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Now I have a complete understanding of the codebase. Let me analyze what needs to be done:\n\n**Current Architecture:**\n- Jakarta EE 10 application with JSF (Faces), EJB, JPA, CDI\n- Open Liberty server\n- H2 in-memory database\n- WAR packaging\n- JSF-based UI with XHTML templates\n\n**Migration Strategy:**\nThe app is a JSF-based CRUD address book. Quarkus doesn't support JSF natively. The best approach is to convert this to a **JAX-RS REST API** with Quarkus + Hibernate ORM (Panache) + H2. The CRUD functionality (Create, Read, Update, Delete contacts) will be exposed as REST endpoints instead of JSF pages.\n\nLet me proceed with the migration:"}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":4867,"cache_read_input_tokens":30865,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":4867,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":639},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"a4d68ab5-7a1d-4b4a-ab1e-eeb798077cae","uuid":"63606bee-31c7-4bab-9020-fc1b9543c762"}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_bdrk_016WeL5FuhndScHFuSyyFHrX","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_bdrk_01Qx2nZ7tnjWM8otQeR5YNf8","name":"TodoWrite","input":{"todos":[{"content":"Analyze existing codebase structure","status":"completed","activeForm":"Analyzing existing codebase structure"},{"content":"Create new pom.xml with Quarkus dependencies","status":"in_progress","activeForm":"Creating new pom.xml with Quarkus dependencies"},{"content":"Rewrite Contact entity for Quarkus/Hibernate ORM","status":"pending","activeForm":"Rewriting Contact entity"},{"content":"Create Panache repository to replace EJB facade","status":"pending","activeForm":"Creating Panache repository"},{"content":"Create JAX-RS REST resource to replace JSF controller","status":"pending","activeForm":"Creating JAX-RS REST resource"},{"content":"Create application.properties for Quarkus config","status":"pending","activeForm":"Creating application.properties"},{"content":"Remove obsolete JSF/Liberty/EJB files","status":"pending","activeForm":"Removing obsolete files"},{"content":"Update Dockerfile for Quarkus","status":"pending","activeForm":"Updating Dockerfile"},{"content":"Generate smoke tests","status":"pending","activeForm":"Generating smoke tests"},{"content":"Build Docker image and run container","status":"pending","activeForm":"Building Docker image and running container"},{"content":"Execute smoke tests and fix issues","status":"pending","activeForm":"Executing smoke tests and fixing issues"},{"content":"Document all actions in CHANGELOG.md","status":"pending","activeForm":"Documenting actions in CHANGELOG.md"}]}}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":4867,"cache_read_input_tokens":30865,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":4867,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":639},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_