{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_bdrk_01Xt9mE9qUwyXvYJc7MPNrpt","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\n\n## Migration Summary\n\n**Frameworks:** Jakarta EE 10 (JSF + EJB + JPA on Open Liberty) -> Quarkus 3.17.8 (REST + Hibernate ORM Panache)\n\n**Outcome: SUCCESS** - All 13 smoke tests passed, application builds and runs correctly.\n\n### High-level actions:\n1. Replaced Jakarta EE WAR application with Quarkus JAR application\n2. Converted JSF/EJB layer to JAX-RS REST API with Panache active record pattern\n3. Retained all CRUD business logic and validation rules\n4. Configured H2 in-memory database via Quarkus properties\n\n### File Tree\n\n```\nModified:\n- pom.xml: Replaced Jakarta EE/Liberty deps with Quarkus BOM and extensions\n- Dockerfile: Changed from Liberty run to Quarkus JAR execution\n- .dockerignore: Removed exclusions for Maven wrapper files\n- src/main/java/jakarta/tutorial/addressbook/entity/Contact.java: Converted to PanacheEntity\n- src/main/resources/application.properties: New Quarkus configuration\n\nAdded:\n- src/main/java/jakarta/tutorial/addressbook/rest/ContactResource.java: JAX-RS REST resource\n- smoke.py: 13 smoke tests for CRUD operations\n- CHANGELOG.md: Migration documentation\n\nRemoved:\n- src/main/java/jakarta/tutorial/addressbook/ejb/AbstractFacade.java: EJB generic facade\n- src/main/java/jakarta/tutorial/addressbook/ejb/ContactFacade.java: EJB stateless bean\n- src/main/java/jakarta/tutorial/addressbook/web/ContactController.java: JSF managed bean\n- src/main/java/jakarta/tutorial/addressbook/web/util/JsfUtil.java: JSF utility\n- src/main/java/jakarta/tutorial/addressbook/web/util/PaginationHelper.java: JSF pagination helper\n- src/main/resources/META-INF/persistence.xml: JPA config (replaced by application.properties)\n- src/main/webapp/ (entire directory): JSF XHTML templates, web.xml, faces-config.xml, CSS\n- src/main/liberty/ (entire directory): Open Liberty server.xml\n```\n\n### Step-by-Step Log\n\n```\n[2026-03-17T00:50:00Z] [info] Analyzed project structure - Jakarta EE 10 Address Book on Open Liberty\n[2026-03-17T00:51:00Z] [info] Determined migration strategy - JSF->REST, EJB->Panache, JPA retained\n[2026-03-17T00:52:00Z] [info] Updated pom.xml - Quarkus 3.17.8 BOM, 7 extensions added\n[2026-03-17T00:53:00Z] [info] Refactored Contact.java - PanacheEntity active record pattern\n[2026-03-17T00:54:00Z] [info] Created ContactResource.java - JAX-RS REST endpoints for CRUD\n[2026-03-17T00:54:30Z] [info] Created application.properties - H2 datasource, Hibernate config\n[2026-03-17T00:55:00Z] [info] Removed 5 obsolete Java files, 3 XML configs, 5 XHTML templates\n[2026-03-17T00:55:30Z] [info] Updated Dockerfile - Quarkus JAR execution\n[2026-03-17T00:56:00Z] [info] Created smoke.py - 13 CRUD smoke tests\n[2026-03-17T00:56:30Z] [info] Docker build succeeded on first attempt\n[2026-03-17T00:56:50Z] [info] Container started - Quarkus booted in 2.619s\n[2026-03-17T00:56:55Z] [warning] Removed unrecognized config key quarkus.jackson.date-format\n[2026-03-17T00:57:00Z] [info] All 13/13 smoke tests passed\n```\n\n### Error Handling\n\n- **Warnings:** 1 warning about unrecognized `quarkus.jackson.date-format` config key - resolved by removing it\n- **Critical Issues:** None\n- **Manual Intervention Required:** None"}],"stop_reason":"end_turn","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":461,"cache_read_input_tokens":71876,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":461,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":1064},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"a4d68ab5-7a1d-4b4a-ab1e-eeb798077cae","uuid":"45fb3015-cfdc-4328-8df2-24522707f003"}
